<section id="about" class="py-24 px-6 border-t border-white/5">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-start">
      <!-- Left: text -->
      <div>
        <p class="text-[#f5a623] text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest mb-4">About</p>
        <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black tracking-tight mb-8">
          Built by someone<br />
          <span class="text-[#f5a623]">who's been there.</span>
        </h2>
        <div class="space-y-4 text-white/60 text-lg leading-relaxed">
          <p>
            Media Map was founded by <strong class="text-white">Tom Andrews</strong> — a producer
            and composer with over 25 years in the film and television industry.
          </p>
          <p>
            Tom's music credits include <em>Neighbours</em>, <em>City Homicide</em>, and
            <em>The Secret Life of Us</em>. His production work spans Warner Brothers, Channel 7, 9,
            10, ABC, Fox, Eureka Productions, and Endemol Shine.
          </p>
          <p>
            He's been on set, in the edit suite, and in the studio. He knows where the pain points
            are — and he knows which AI tools actually help.
          </p>
          <p class="text-white/40 text-base">
            Media Map exists because the AI landscape is overwhelming and the media industry deserves
            honest, practical guidance from people who understand the craft.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Right: stat blocks -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4 mt-8 md:mt-16">
        <div class="bg-white/[0.03] border border-white/5 rounded-2xl p-6">
          <div class="text-4xl font-black text-[#f5a623] mb-2">25+</div>
          <div class="text-white/50 text-sm">Years in Film & Television</div>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white/[0.03] border border-white/5 rounded-2xl p-6">
          <div class="text-4xl font-black text-[#f5a623] mb-2">10+</div>
          <div class="text-white/50 text-sm">Major Networks & Studios</div>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white/[0.03] border border-white/5 rounded-2xl p-6 col-span-2">
          <div class="text-2xl font-black text-white mb-2">"We let creators get back to creating."</div>
          <div class="text-white/40 text-sm">— The Media Map philosophy</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
